title: Grateful Dead Live at The Centrum on 1987-04-03

Set 1

Hell In A Bucket  ->
Sugaree  
C C Rider  
It Must Have Been The Roses

Set 2

Wharf Rat  ->

Not Fade Away  

Encore
U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: Go Joe Joe always puts up good audiences, I like his tapes. This show sounds great. I think its the best of the aud. sources for this show. Thanks Joe for taping this show and the hundred others you uploaded to LMA.
